thread.title: Els Comeyne

author: Els Comeyne
title: Els Comeyne
text: I spend a week in Tenerife with two lovely cats and seaview. Quiet, local town and close to little port and beach with lots of places to eat and natural park. Andrea, the house owner is supernice, i arrived with a cold and she made me fantastic fresh fruitjuice. There is a local market where you can buy fruit and vegetables grown by local farmers.
